  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I've heard that you’ve become quite the weaponcrafter, and I want to see for myself if the rumors are true. Judging by your tools and your confidence, it seems you’ve built up a fair bit of skill. Care to show me?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Perfect timing! I actually needed a tool for some repairs in my bathroom—lucky me, haha! Go defeat #r#o24#s#k and craft #ba #t1422003##k, then bring it back. #o24#s can be found around #m10001000#, so it shouldn’t be too difficult. I’ll be waiting!"
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Looks like you haven’t quite reached that level of skill, have you?"
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Let’s see… this is remarkably well made. I’m genuinely impressed you’ve reached this level of craftsmanship. Yes, this is the quality expected of a true weaponcrafter. Your dedication to honing your skills is admirable. Looks like I owe you a special reward."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "This #t4130000# is a unique item that can alter an equipment’s stats when used during crafting. It’s very unstable, so sometimes the results may be disappointing—but if handled well, it might create something far beyond your expectations."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "If you want to test the limits of your weaponcrafting skill, I highly recommend giving it a try. Just… don’t blame me if the results aren’t what you hoped for, hahaha!"
        }
      },
